column1: Besides TGFbeta and RTK / Ras signaling, autocrine factors and Wnt -, Notch -, Hedgehog - and NF - kappaB - dependent pathways were found to contribute to EMT.
Brain pericytes in culture had higher levels of endosialin / TEM 1 than TEMs - 2, - 3, - 4, - 5, - 7, and - 8.
The epidermal growth factor receptor ( EGF - R, c - erbB1), Her - 2 / neu ( c - erbB2), and c - erbB3 are members of the erbB - family.
